-- AirAsia Chief Tony Fernandes Considers Virgin Atlantic Bid, Times Reports
-- B y   M i c h e l l e   E .   F r a z e r
-- 2010-12-26T12:07:46Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-26/airasia-ceo-considering-virgin-atlantic-bid-sunday-times-says.html
AirAsia Bhd . Chief Executive Officer
 Tony Fernandes  is considering a takeover bid for Virgin Atlantic
Airways Ltd., the Sunday Times reported, without saying where it
got the information.  Virgin spokesman Greg Dawson confirmed earlier this month
that the U.K. carrier received "a number of lines of enquiry"
since it hired Deutsche Bank AG to explore options.  To contact the reporter on this story:
